column1: "S Hill" and "Hill" seem to be the same person, just switches to "Hill" after first introduction of "S Hill." Same with "S Moore" and "Moore."
"S Hill" and "A Hill" seem to be different people, based on the handwriting.
"Jones" written on top of "Gibbs" (or vice versa) at 5:30 p.m. on 7/29/2023
